# Optional dependencies provide enhanced features with automatic fallbacks:
#
# better-sqlite3: SQLite storage (faster than JSON)
#   - Falls back to JSON file storage if unavailable
#   - May fail on Termux/Android due to native compilation
#
# bedrock-protocol: Minecraft Bedrock Edition support
#   - Falls back to Java Edition only if unavailable
#   - May fail on Termux/Android due to native compilation
#
# node-llama-cpp: Local AI model support via llama.cpp
#   - Falls back to Ollama or built-in rules if unavailable
#   - May fail on Termux/Android due to native compilation
#
# All features have graceful fallbacks - the app works on any platform!
